---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Autism & Routines: Building Structure That Supports Regulation | Neurosage Hub"
  description="Why predictable routines are a regulation tool for autistic children — how to build, protect, and adapt routines that reduce anxiety and support daily functioning."
>
  <Header />

  <main>

    <section class="py-20" style="background:#082438;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <nav class="mb-6">
            <a href="/resources" style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:0.8125rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration:none;">← Resources</a>
          </nav>
          <p class="nsh-eyebrow mb-4 fade-up" style="color:#D8896A;">Hub</p>
          <h1 class="fade-up mb-5" style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem); color:white; line-height:1.1;">
            Routines
          </h1>
          <p class="fade-up" style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:1.125rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height:1.7; max-width:34rem;">
            Routines aren't just helpful for autistic children — they're a core nervous system regulation strategy. Predictability reduces anxiety, conserves cognitive energy, and creates the safety a child needs to learn and grow.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16" style="background:white;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="rounded-2xl p-12 fade-up" style="background:#F7F2EB; border:1px solid #ddd9d2;">
            <p class="nsh-eyebrow mb-3" style="color:#7B9E8B;">Coming soon</p>
            <h2 style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:1.375rem; color:#082438; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Routines guides are on the way</h2>
            <p style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#5F6975; line-height:1.75; max-width:28rem; margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">
              We're building guides on morning and bedtime routines, transition strategies, visual schedules, and how to handle routine disruptions without a meltdown.
            </p>
            <a href="/resources" style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:0.875rem; font-weight:600; color:#2E6E8E; text-decoration:none;">← Back to all resources</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16" style="background:#082438;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
          <p class="nsh-eyebrow mb-3" style="color:#D8896A;">Neurosage Hub</p>
          <h2 style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3.5vw,2.125rem); color:white; margin-bottom:0.875rem; line-height:1.25;">Get started today</h2>
          <p style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:1rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); max-width:28rem; margin:0 auto 2rem; line-height:1.7;">
            The Neurosage Hub Platform is built around structured, repeatable activities — giving families an easy daily routine that builds progress over time.
          </p>
          <a href="/family-sign-up" style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:0.9375rem; font-weight:700; background:#D8896A; color:white; padding:0.875rem 2rem; border-radius:9999px; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">
            Get Started Free
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
